snippet.description:
And so, I became yours, before I was even myself. The melody wrote the words, the words sang the melody, as if everything was to always return to find me as yours. As time refused to change directions, space bent itself to place me in front of you so I could fall in love the way love was meant to be fallen into.

In one way or the other, in some time or another, as I have found myself in front of you, I shall always find myself as yours.

For Maya, always.
